nodes.text: Ord Biniir was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories, in grid square K-5 on the Standard Galactic Grid. Prior to the Galactic Civil War, the Alliance to Restore the Republic launched a successful assault on Imperial targets there. However the resulting victory did not show the full potency of the rebellion.
Ord Biniir was first mentioned in the 2016 roleplaying game Star Wars: The Force Awakens Beginner Game.
